\c 2
\s Kutonga kwaJehovha pamusoro peJerusaremu
\p
\v 1 Ishe akafukidza sei mukunda welioni negore rokutsamwa kwake! Akabvisa kunaka kwalsiraeri akazvikandira pasi, akasarangarira chitsiko chake nezuva rokutsamwa kwake.
\p
\v 2 Ishe akaparadza ugaro hwose hwaJakobho, akasanzwira tsitsi; pakutsamwa kwake akawisira pasi nhare dzomukunda waJudha; akadziwisira pasi; akamhura ushe namachinda ahwo.
\p
\v 3 Nokutsamwa kukuru akagura nyanga haana kudzosa ruoko rwake pakuparadza; akachemedza nhare norusvingo, zvinopera simba pamwechete.
\p
\v 9 Masuo aro akanyura pasi, akaparadza nokuvhuna zvipfigiso zvaro; mambo waro namachinda aro vari pakati pamarudzi asina murayiro. Zvirokwazvo vaporofita varo havana zvavanoratidzwa naJehovha.
\p
\v 10 Vakuru vomukunda welioni vagere pasi, vanoramba vanyerere; vakakushira guruva pamisoro yavo, vakazvisunga zviuno namasaga; mhandara dzeJerusaremu dzakakotamisa misoro yadzo pasi.
\p
\v 11 Meso angu apera nemisodzi, mwoyo wangu unotambudzika; chiropa changu chadururirwa pasi, nemhaka yokuparadzwa kwomukunda wavanhu vangu, nokuti vanana navanoyamwa vanoziya munzira dzomuguta.
\p
\v 12 Vanoti kuna madzimai avo, "Zviyo newaini zviripiko?" Vachingoziya munzira dzomuguta savakakuvadzwa, mweya yavo ichidururirwa pachipfuva chamadzimai avo.
\p
\v 13 Ndichakupupureiko? Ndichakufananidza nei, iwe mukunda weJerusaremu? Ndichakuenzanisa nei, kuti ndikunyaradze, iwe mhandara mukunda welioni? Nokuti pawakaparadzwa pakakura segungwa, ndiani achakuporesa?
\p
\v 14 Vaporofita vako vakakuonera zviratidzo zvenhema nezvoupenzi; havana kubudisa zvakaipa zvako, kuti vadzose kutapwa kwako, asi vakakuonera zvirevo zvenhema nezvinokutapisa.
\p
\v 15 Vose vanopfuura vachaita nondo pamusoro pako, vanoridza muridzo nokudzungudzira mukunda weJerusaremu misoro yavo, vachiti, "Ko ndiro guta rainzi navanhu
\ rakanaka-naka kwazvo, mufaro wenyika yose?"
\p
\v 16 Vavengi vako vose
\s vakakushamisira miromo yavo; vanoridza muridzo nokugeda-geda meno,
\s vanoti, "Tariparadza; zvirokwazvo ndiro
\s zuva ratakanga takatarira;
\s tariwana, tariona."
\p
\v 17 Jehovha akaita izvo zvaakafunga, akapedzisa shoko rake raakaraira pamazuva akare;
\s akawisira pasi, akasava netsitsi; akafadza muvengi pamusoro pako, akasimudza runyanga rwavadzivisi
\s vako.
\p
\v 18 Mwoyo yavo yakadana kuna Ishe. Iwe rusvingo rwomukunda welioni, misodzi ngaiyerere sorwizi
\s masikati nousiku,
\s usazorora, mboni yeziso rako isarega kuchema.
\p
\v 19 Muka, danidzira usiku,
\s pakutanga kwenguva dzose;
\s durura mwoyo wako semvura pamberi paJehovha;
\s simudzira maoko ako kwaari nokuda
\s kwoupenyu hwavana vako,
\s vanoziya nenzara pakuvamba kwenzira imwe neimwe yomuguta.
\p
\v 20 Tarirai, Jehovha, muone
\s vamakaitira zvakadai!
\s Ko vakadzi vangadye zvibereko zvavo,
\s ivo vana vari pamaoko here? Ko vapristi navaporofita
\s vangaurawe
\s panzvimbo tsvene yaishe here?
\p
\v 21 Majaya navatana vavete pasi munzira dzomuguta;
\s mhandara dzangu namajaya angu vaurawa nomunondo;
\s makavauraya nezuva rokutsamwa kwenyu,
\s makavabaya, hamuna kuvanzwira tsitsi.
\p
\v 22 Makadaidza zvinondityisa pamativi ose,
\s sapazuva reungano yakatarwa;
\s hakuna akapukunyuka kana akasara pazuva rokutsamwa kwaJehovha; vandakabata mumaoko
\s navandakarera
\s vapedzwa nomuvengi wangu.
\s dzose dzaIsiraeri;
\s akadzosa ruoko rwake rworudyi pamberi pomuvengi,
\s akapisa munaJakobho somurazvo womoto
\s unopedza zvose kumativi ose.
\p
\v 4 Akakunga uta hwake somuvengi, akamira noruoko rwake
\s somudzivisi,
\s akauraya vose vaifadza meso; akadurura kutsamwa kwake somoto patende romukunda welioni.
\p
\v 5 Ishe wava somuvengi,
\s akamedza Isiraeri;
\s akamedza dzimba dzavo dzose dzoushe,
\s akaparadza nhare dzavo; akawanzira mukunda waJudha kuchema nokurira.
\p
\v 6 Akabvisa ruzhowa rwake nesimba sorwomunda;
\s akaparadza nzvimbo yake yokuungana;
\s Jehovha akakanganwisa paZioni ungano yakatarwa neSabata, akashora madzimambo navapristi neshungu dzokutsamwa kwake.
\p
\v 7 Jehovha akarasa atari yake, akasema nzvimbo yake tsvene, akaisa masvingo edzimba dzavo
\s Câ€˜/ONISk\t Mima.oko omuN eixg;v, vakaita bope mumba maJehovha, sapazuva reungano yakatarwa.
\p
\v 8 Jehovha akafunga kuparadza rusvingo rwomukunda welioni; akatatanura rwonzi rwokuyera,
